"FAQ_WHAT_IS_THIS_A" = "This program was developed by the Furman Institute of Running and Scientific Training (FIRST) and was featured in the Runner's World magazine. The author, Amby Burfoot, is a famous American marathon runner who won the 1968 Boston Marathon. So far many FIRST has helped many runners improve their race finish times.";
